title: A Cafe By ChefauChef
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe and catering, at this location since Jun 2014. Offers breakfast and lunch. Vegan choices include a vegan value meal which changes weekly, a skinny salad, side salad, a few sides, and a voluptuous veggies wrap. Soup of the moment sometimes is vegan. Beverages are juice, coffee, tea, and soda.
